data.description: Come tour this beauty with a fantastic view of the lake with the last lot that allows you to build a deck on to it! 4 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with high ceilings and loads of natural light...you're going to love this space! Walk through the front door and you'll be greeted with a gorgeous view of the lake immediately through all of the windows on the back side of the home. The living room is spacious with a cozy fireplace for the chilly winter evenings. To the left you'll see the formal dining room with beautiful lighting and a large window. Next up you'll see the kitchen with stainless appliances, beautiful wood cabinetry and brand new windows to view the lake while you're cooking! From there you'll see the spare bath with a large soaking tub, and then 2 spare bedrooms with great space and perfect closets! Walk upstairs and you'll be greeted by the 4th bedroom which could serve as a wonderful bonus or office space, even a work out room with an attached half bath! On your way downstairs, stop and enjoy some time in your new backyard with that relaxing view and then take a tour of your new master with tray ceilings, a large bedroom as well as a wonderful view of the lake. Step into the master bath and you'll notice the gorgeous wood cabinetry, dual sinks, a massive jetted tub with hand sprayer and a separate custom tile shower to boot! Spring Lake features walking nature trails and play areas for you and your family, plus pods to fish! Flood zone X and has never flooded.
